cr = classification_report(y_true=test_df["scrap"], y_pred=preds, output_dict=True)
cr_1dconv = classification_report(y_true=test_df["scrap"], y_pred=preds_1dconv, output_dict=True)

model_names = ["autoencoder", "autoencoder_with_1dconv"]
c_reports = [cr, cr_1dconv]
metrics = ["precision", "recall", "f1-score"]
classes = ["0", "1"]

df_combined = pd.DataFrame()

for model_name, cr in zip(model_names, c_reports):
    for metric in metrics:
        for class_label in classes:
            value = cr[class_label][metric]
            df_combined.loc[f"{metric} - {class_label.split()[-1]}", model_name] = value
            
df_combined
